Package edu.umn.nlpie.mtap.processing

Annotation Type LabelIndexDescription

@Documented
@Target(TYPE)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface LabelIndexDescription
A description of the input and output label indices of a processor.

  • Optional Element Summary

    Optional Elements 
    Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
    java.lang.String description
    A description of the label index.
    java.lang.String name
    The default name of the label index.
    java.lang.String nameFromParameter
    If the name comes from a parameter, the key for that parameter.
    boolean optional
    Whether the label index is an optional input.
    PropertyDescription[] properties
    The properties of the labels.
    java.lang.String reference
    If this is an output of another processor, that processor's name followed by a slash and the default output name of the index go here.

  • Element Details

    • name

      java.lang.String name
      The default name of the label index.
      Returns:
      A label index name identifier.
      Default:
      ""

    • reference

      java.lang.String reference
      If this is an output of another processor, that processor's name followed by a slash and the default output name of the index go here. Example: "sentence-detector/sentences".
      Returns:
      A string reference.
      Default:
      ""

    • nameFromParameter

      java.lang.String nameFromParameter
      If the name comes from a parameter, the key for that parameter.
      Returns:
      A string key.
      Default:
      ""

    • optional

      boolean optional
      Whether the label index is an optional input.
      Returns:
      True if optional, false if required.
      Default:
      false

    • description

      java.lang.String description
      A description of the label index.
      Returns:
      String description of the label index.
      Default:
      ""

    • properties

      PropertyDescription[] properties
      The properties of the labels.
      Returns:
      array of PropertyDescription
      Default:
      {}
